1935;;1,000 Dollars a Minute;;American;;Aubrey Scotto;;Leila Hyams, Edward Brophy;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/1,000_Dollars_a_Minute;;A broken and pennyless newspaperman takes part in an experiment where two crazy millionaires are offering a prize of $10,000 to anyone that can spend $1,000 a minute, every minute, for 12 hours straight.